t-7xl text-white  mb-6 tracking-wider\" data-astro-cid-u4qoyrkz=\"true\"> \nNUESTROS ARTISTAS\n </h2>  <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\" data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistsSection.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"15:74\">\nConoce a los talentosos artistas que dan vida a tus ideas. Cada uno con su estilo único y años de experiencia.\n</p> </div> <!-- Grid de artistas individuales --> <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16\" data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistsSection.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"21:65\"> <div class=\"scroll-animate\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\" data-delay=\"0.2\" data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistsSection.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"22:76\"> <div class=\"artist-card group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-black border border-gray-800 hover:border-amber-400/50 transition-all duration-500 \" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"13:202\"> <!-- Background with overlay --> <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent z-10\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"15:4\"></div> <!-- Artist Image --> <div class=\"relative h-96 md:h-[500px] overflow-hidden\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"18:59\"> <picture class=\"block\" data-astro-cid-ljn3pzdo data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ImageOptimized.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"49:24\"> <!-- WebP/AVIF para navegadores compatibles --> <source srcset=\"/artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=320&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp 320w, /artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=640&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp 640w, /artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=768&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 33vw\" type=\"image/webp\" data-astro-cid-ljn3pzdo data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ImageOptimized.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"60:8\">  <!-- Imagen fallback --> <img src=\"/artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=400&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp\" srcset=\"/artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=320&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp 320w, /artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=640&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp 640w, /artists/david/artist-david.jpg?w=768&#38;q=80&#38;f=webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1200px) 50vw, 33vw\" alt=\"David - Especialista en Tatuajes Realistas\" width=\"400\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out opacity-0 scale-95 w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out\" data-optimized-image data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt=\"true\" data-astro-cid-ljn3pzdo data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ImageOptimized.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"69:4\"> </picture> <script>\n  // Sistema de lazy loading personalizado con IntersectionObserver\n  if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {\n    const imageObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries, observer) => {\n      entries.forEach(entry => {\n        if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n          const img = entry.target;\n          \n          // Aplicar animación de entrada\n          img.classList.remove('opacity-0', 'scale-95');\n          img.classList.add('opacity-100', 'scale-100');\n          \n          // Dejar de observar esta imagen\n          observer.unobserve(img);\n        }\n      });\n    }, {\n      rootMargin: '50px 0px',\n      threshold: 0.1\n    });\n\n    // Observar todas las imágenes optimizadas\n    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n      const images = document.querySelectorAll('[data-optimized-image]');\n      images.forEach(img => {\n        if (img.loading === 'lazy') {\n          imageObserver.observe(img);\n        } else {\n          // Para imágenes eager, aplicar animación inmediatamente\n          img.classList.add('opacity-100', 'scale-100');\n        }\n      });\n    });\n  } else {\n    // Fallback para navegadores sin IntersectionObserver\n    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n      const images = document.querySelectorAll('[data-optimized-image]');\n      images.forEach(img => {\n        img.classList.add('opacity-100', 'scale-100');\n      });\n    });\n  }\n</script>  </div> <!-- Content --> <div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6 md:p-8 z-20\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"30:65\"> <!-- Artist Name --> <h3 class=\"font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white  mb-2\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt=\"true\" data-astro-cid-u4qoyrkz=\"true\"> \nDavid\n </h3>  <!-- Specialty --> <p class=\"text-amber-400 font-semibold text-lg mb-3\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"37:58\">\nEspecialista en Realismo\n</p> <!-- Description --> <p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm md:text-base mb-4 line-clamp-3 group-hover:line-clamp-none transition-all duration-300\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"42:125\">\nMás de 8 años de experiencia en tatuajes realistas y retratos. \n      David domina las técnicas de sombreado y detalle que dan vida a cada diseño. \n      Especializado en retratos, animales y naturaleza muerta con un nivel de detalle excepcional.\n</p> <!-- Specialties List --> <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"49:44\"> <span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-amber-400/10 text-amber-400 text-xs rounded-full border border-amber-400/20\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"50:110\">\nRetratos\n</span> <span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-amber-400/10 text-amber-400 text-xs rounded-full border border-amber-400/20\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"53:110\">\nRealismo\n</span> <span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-amber-400/10 text-amber-400 text-xs rounded-full border border-amber-400/20\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"56:110\">\nAnimales\n</span> <span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-amber-400/10 text-amber-400 text-xs rounded-full border border-amber-400/20\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"59:110\">\nNaturaleza Muerta\n</span> </div> <!-- Stats --> <div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6 text-center\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"65:58\"> <div data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"66:12\"> <div class=\"text-amber-400 font-bold text-lg\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"67:55\">8+</div> <div class=\"text-gray-400 text-xs\" data-astro-cid-f4gsfsmt data-astro-source-file=\"/workspaces/cubatattoostudio/src/components/ArtistDavid.astro\" data-astro-source-loc=\"68:44\">Años</div> </div> <div data-astro-cid-